    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界已被摧毁，生存的可能性越来越小……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为幸存者，你必须奋力生存一天，然后逃往生活尚存之地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能坚持多久呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>前哨站</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名游牧者，你并不孤单，始终可以与其他幸存者交易，并通过完成任务进行合作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/87c649db688d42998fc2af4a8bae12a9.avif?t=1760886099\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras_big/87c649db688d42998fc2af4a8bae12a9.avif?t=1760886099 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/f08011c35033c47f07ac25ddeacb68bb.avif?t=1760886099\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras_big/f08011c35033c47f07ac25ddeacb68bb.avif?t=1760886099 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掠夺</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的场景和僵尸中搜刮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/1ae8b5dc0c372d7823f72af7b00a75c0.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/1ae8b5dc0c372d7823f72af7b00a75c0.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/1ae8b5dc0c372d7823f72af7b00a75c0.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>_____</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >耕作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从环境中收集材料制作物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/6c3fc6dfa5b11561a5bb71782058ed66.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/6c3fc6dfa5b11561a5bb71782058ed66.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/6c3fc6dfa5b11561a5bb71782058ed66.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用逐步制作系统，制作能帮你生存的物品，一旦失败，将会通过减少物品质量作为惩罚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/552982d9c043a8abe0a2e0ce4aa58237.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/552982d9c043a8abe0a2e0ce4aa58237.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/552982d9c043a8abe0a2e0ce4aa58237.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >程序生成的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越程序生成的地图逃离污染。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/00a58f17185c58de355ff64e1f883328.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/00a58f17185c58de355ff64e1f883328.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/00a58f17185c58de355ff64e1f883328.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >车辆（可定制）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修理和定制车辆，使你能够旅行并具备杀伤力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/45a1520bf965f15c39e0532cbcb22f74.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/45a1520bf965f15c39e0532cbcb22f74.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/45a1520bf965f15c39e0532cbcb22f74.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >防御建筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用不同效果的墙壁和陷阱巩固你的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/0baf18444d2f4bd85541aad3fcda5d80.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/0baf18444d2f4bd85541aad3fcda5d80.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/0baf18444d2f4bd85541aad3fcda5d80.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >僵尸群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抵御数量、强度和速度都随着时间和污染水平而增强的僵尸群，你必须为它们做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/b1e0dabe46e68adb18b754939f4ba050.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/b1e0dabe46e68adb18b754939f4ba050.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/b1e0dabe46e68adb18b754939f4ba050.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
